### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### PUSH
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Suscribir a push
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/push/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endpoint": "https://...",
  "keys": {
    "p256dh": "...",
    "auth": "..."
  }
}

### Desuscribir de push
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/push/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endpoint": "https://..."
}

